high_descs: Turn right and walk to the toilet.
Take the pump bottle off of the toilet tank.
Walk ahead and veer left to the sink on the right side of the counter.
Place the bottle in the bottom right cabinet to the left of the candle closest to you.
Turn right and look into the red bin.
Take the pump bottle out of the red bin.
Turn left and walk back to the sink.
Put the second bottle in the bottom right cabinet to the right of the first bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place two pump bottles in a cabinet.

high_descs: Go forward, then to your left and stop at the toilet
Pick up the soap dispenser that's on top of the toilet tank
Turn back around and go to your left to the right side sink
Open the bottom right cabinet and place the soap inside the front left corner
Turn to your right and look down into the trashcan
Pick up the soap dispenser that's inside the trashcan
Turn to your left and go back over to the right side sink
Place soap into the bottom right cabinet, on the right of the other soap
anns.task_desc: Store away two soap dispensers under the sink

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the toilet.
Pick up the soap on top of the toilet.
Turn the left and face the sink on top of the cabinet.
Place the soap in the cabinet under the sink .
Turn to the right and face the trash can.
Pick up the soap from the trash can.
Turn to the left and face the cabinet under the sink.
Place the soap in the cabinet under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the soaps in the cabinet under the sink.
